channel.title: Public voids, how to add? And what they are?
channel.description:
Ok, so I'm TRYING to make a mini-game but I realized that I can't make an object without using PUBLIC VOIDS or VOIDS or w/e they are can some one explain me what Public voids are and how to add them?
:D Thanks!

item.title: Public voids, how to add? And what they are?
item.dc:creator: @hanif hanif
item.description:
@hanif wrote:

[quote=“I Br3ndan I, post:2, topic:100016”]To add a public void you simply search for this (I’m assuming inside you’re client.Java);

public void

Under the last brace (}) hit return and add yours. The brace shows that it’s the end of the void.[/quote]

Thx I Br3ndan I

Read full topic
item.source: Public voids, how to add? And what they are?
